---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="No Rest For The Wicked Wiki"
  description="Community wiki for No Rest For The Wicked items, refinement, and guides."
>
  <main class="mx-auto flex min-h-screen max-w-5xl flex-col gap-10 px-6 py-16">
    <header class="space-y-4">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-slate-400">
        Community-led game wiki
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-white md:text-6xl">
        No Rest For The Wicked
      </h1>
      <p class="max-w-2xl text-lg text-slate-300">
        Track rare drops, item refinement, crafting steps, and where to find
        everything across the Isles.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Starter docs</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Fresh research, ready for edits</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        <a
          class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-6 transition hover:border-slate-600"
          href="/overview"
        >
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Overview</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
            What the game is, who makes it, and where it lives today.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a
          class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-6 transition hover:border-slate-600"
          href="/story-and-setting"
        >
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Story &amp; Setting</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
            The 841 timeline, Isola Sacra, and the Pestilence crisis.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a
          class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-6 transition hover:border-slate-600"
          href="/gameplay"
        >
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Gameplay</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
            Combat cadence, exploration flow, and long-term systems.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a
          class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-6 transition hover:border-slate-600"
          href="/early-access"
        >
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Early Access</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
            Current status, roadmap focus, and how to help the wiki.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Items & Drops</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
          Learn where to farm specific weapons, armor, and materials.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Refinement</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
          Map the exact refinements and upgrade paths for every tier.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Guides</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
          Curated builds, progression tips, and boss strategies.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/70 p-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Get started</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
        Add your first item entry or begin a refinement guide. We will wire up
        content collections next.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">
        Build the first entry
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
